{"tid":1126201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 車場工人1.5米高拖架墮地　重創昏迷","createTime":"2019-04-26T08:07:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T10:51:10.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6d7d915ca2b4efeceb074184ae03d57e450d8efc","tid":1126201,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T08:07:36.000Z","msg":"打鼓嶺文錦渡路一個車場，昨晚（25日）8時許，一名姓霍（63歲）工人在一輛貨櫃車的拖架上工作時，突然跌落1.5米地上，再被玻璃割傷手部，未幾陷入昏迷，工友報警。救護員將霍送北區醫院，因傷勢嚴重，需轉送威爾斯親王醫院進一步救治，目前情況危殆。警方初步調查後，相信事件無可疑，列為工業意外處理，並通知勞工處跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190426/bkn-20190426001211284-0426_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190426%2Fbkn-20190426001211284-0426_00822_001.html&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3TjgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=636c4f4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190426/bkn-20190426001211284-0426_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5de38806c93c9261967f0d316b764f6b5e78d267","tid":1126201,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T08:08:52.000Z","msg":"個別事件"},{"pid":"1c6f18e3c955db487040237075eee99764d7c723","tid":1126201,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5de38806c93c9261967f0d316b764f6b5e78d267","tid":1126201,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T08:08:52.000Z","msg":"個別事件"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T08:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b319ca030610b12e4df64196987284d00946654","tid":1126201,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c6f18e3c955db487040237075eee99764d7c723","tid":1126201,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5de38806c93c9261967f0d316b764f6b5e78d267","tid":1126201,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T08:08:52.000Z","msg":"個別事件"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T08:12:37.000